                <li>üéµ Generative music based on portfolio metrics</li>
                <li>‚öõÔ∏è Quantum mechanics metaphors for finance</li>
                <li>üéÆ Interactive experiences, not static charts</li>
                <li>üì± Multi-platform (Web, VR, Mobile)</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="tech-stack">
                <span class="tech-badge">WebGL</span>
                <span class="tech-badge">Real-time APIs</span>
                <span class="tech-badge">Machine Learning</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Market Opportunity -->
      <section class="slide">
        <div class="slide-content">
          <h2>Market Opportunity</h2>
          <div class="market-analysis">
            <div class="market-size">
              <h3>Total Addressable Market (TAM)</h3>
